{"tid":683464,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] 狼人Spyfall牛頭王Dixit 遊戲Group","createTime":"2018-05-29T17:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T12:02:26.000Z","uid":86102,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa7562c2c6e2a3ca56cd28fb1664a5f5f35e399","tid":683464,"uid":86102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"係啦無錯又係我啦<br />\n一個月都無我又要開多次post 招返啲新血啦<br />\n啱清左啲潛水人員 宜家希望你都可以加入一齊玩啦<br />\n下面呢堆野照copy 唔好介意<br />\n<br />\n以前同中學同學用Telegram個陣只係得狼人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估唔到過左一段時間 狼人都已經多左咁多新角色<br />\n仲新出好多唔同既Bot 有唔同既game玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好可惜 大家成日各有各忙 要返工要返學<br />\n唔係成日聚集到人可以閒時玩一舖Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你都想玩Game可以放鬆下就一齊加入啦<br />\n包括有avalon, 31點, 狼人, 牛頭王 等等<br />\n<br />\n我大概收多十至廿個就會停收人<br />\n所以想入就pm我啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/whylookatme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwhylookatme&d=oJS3i7CeAujLbCyY0SqywTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=92a02b22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/whylookatme</a>"},{"pid":"becb67c0cd4f6948335dd2ecb059c7f5591401ab","tid":683464,"uid":86102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"今晚定晚十點開game"},{"pid":"7b8b2f3fb5daac287e74a51d28ddd34815c282eb","tid":683464,"uid":86102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每晚定時十點開game</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9856e61069e3d7811598b16ed31e4a11776216","tid":683464,"uid":86102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"越多人玩就可以越多新角色同新mode"},{"pid":"4136a3d80fd895918d0a3797cb4c90985ee4c7c2","tid":683464,"uid":86102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"臨瞓前一推"},{"pid":